<%= t ".thread" %>:
<%= thread_url(@thread, anchor: dom_id(@message)) %>

<% if @thread.private_to_committee? %>
Only committee members of <%= raw @thread.group.name %> can view
and post messages to this discussion thread.
<% elsif @thread.private_to_group? %>
Only members of <%= raw @thread.group.name %> can view
and post messages to this discussion thread.
<% else %>
Everyone can view this discussion thread and post messages.
<% end %>

